{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*148>}148{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The Jewish People are referred to in Scripture as Hashem’s slaves (Vayikra 25:42), and as 
