{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*98>}98{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The Gold Altar stood inside the Holy confines, whereas the Copper or Outer Altar stood in 
