{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*102>}102{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}This includes the Yom Kippur offerings mentioned in Mishnah I.\par
