{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*107>}107{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}It could be cooked or roasted.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*108>}108{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The blood was applied against the southwestern and northeastern corners of the Altar and 
