{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*109>}109{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The Kohanim received no part of the meat which was burned, but they shared in the hide.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*110>}110{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The communal peaceoffering were the two lambs offered on Shavuos (Vayikra 23:20).\par
