{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*115>}115{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Brought by a person in doubt whether an act he had committed required a sinoffering.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*116>}116{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}See note 108 on Mishnah IV.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*117>}117{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}See note 107 on Mishnah III.\par
