{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*125>}125{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}That day, the following night and the following day.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*126>}126{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The blood was applied on the wall of the Altar which was above the base. [Not all its walls 
