{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*89>}89{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Hashem also helps those who are spiritually impoverished.—Rabbi Yehuda ben Yakar\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*90>}90{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Intrinsically.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*91>}91{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}By others.\par
