their transgression,’ said Adonoy” (Yeshaya 59:20).\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*93>}93{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}While Hashem is always referred to as the Redeemer of Yisrael, this blessing utilizes the 
