{\highlight7 <CH12>}{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*1>}1{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Rabbi Yonasan Eibschitz in his sefer, Yaaros Devash, explains that upon reflecting in Whose 
