sentence reads: {\highlight7 @hh}{\highlight7 <HEB>}\rtlch \'eb\'cc\'c4\'e9 \'e1\'c7\'e9\'cc\'e5\'c9\'ed \'e4\'c7\'e6\'c6\'e4 \'e9\'c0\'eb\'c7\'f4\'cc\'c5\'f8 \'f2\'c2\'ec\'c5\'e9\'eb\'c6\'ed \'ec\'c0\'e8\'c7\'e4\'c5\'f8 \'e0\'c6\'fa\'c0\'eb\'c6\'ed \'ee\'c4\'eb\'cc\'c9\'ec \'e7\'c7\'e8\'c9\'e0\'fa\'c5\'e9\'eb\'c6\'ed{\highlight7 {\ltrch @ee}}{\highlight7 {\ltrch<}{\ltrch ENG}{\ltrch>}}\ltrch . “For on this day He will make atonement 
