\ltrch represent a command to cleanse ourselves before Him, as the Targum says: {\highlight7 @hh}{\highlight7 <HEB>}\rtlch \'e5\'c0\'e0\'c7\'fa\'cc\'e5\'cc\'ef \'f7\'c8\'e3\'c8\'ed \'e4' \'fa\'cc\'e5\'c9\'e3\'e5\'cc\'ef 
