{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*50>}50{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Not obeying their commands, not rising for a talmudic scholar and disrespect for one’s 
teacher even if he is not considered a “Torah Great” are included.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*51>}51{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}This includes using physical, political or financial power to harm someone.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*52>}52{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}This involves any sin committed that becomes public knowledge, including improper 
