—Siddur HaGra\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*57>}57{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}A bribe is not limited to money or gifts; it includes flattery or personal favors.— Siddur 
