{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*59>}59{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Ridicule of a person, a commandment, or guards of Torah are all included in the sin of 
