{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*61>}61{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma Ch. 1:3.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*62>}62{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Ibid. The Mishnah continues, “Perhaps you have forgotten (the service), or perhaps you 
