{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*63>}63{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Ibid. This was done in order to acquaint him with the animals that he would sacrifice the 
