{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*65>}65{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma ch. 1:5. The ritual of taking a handful of incense and bringing it in the Holy 
