{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*66>}66{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Ibid. It is a tradition of the oral law that the incense should be placed on the pan of coals 
