{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*67>}67{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma ch. 1:5. The Rambam writes that it is forbidden by our Torah to suspect 
