{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*71>}71{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma Ch. 2:1. The Terumas Hadeshen was the first service of the day and 
