{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*72>}72{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma Ch. 2:3. According to the Talmud, Yoma 24b, the four choosing’s were not 
