{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*74>}74{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma Ch. 2:4. The third lot to determine who would burn the incense on the inner 
