{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*75>}75{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma Ch. 3:1. A watchman was stationed on a high place in the courtyard (Tifferes 
