{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*76>}76{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma Ch. 3:4. Before putting on the eight garments, he immersed himself in the 
