{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*80>}80{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Ibid. The High Priest performed the minimal cut; the major part of each of the two “signs” 
