{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*135>}135{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma 6:3. After the confession, the High Priest handed the scapegoat over to 
