{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*136>}136{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma 6:6. The goat’s bones were broken before it even reached the bottom of the 
