{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*137>}137{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma 6:7.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*138>}138{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}These parts include the kidneys, part of the liver and certain fats which were offered on the 
