{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*142>}142{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}This refers to the fats of the goat and ox which were burnt outside Yerushalayim. The fats 
