{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*145>}145{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The white garments were used only once, and then they were put away forever.\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*146>}146{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Mishnah Yoma 7:4.\par
