{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*149>}149{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}When the Divine Presence, the “Shechina” is upon a person, his face radiates like a burning 
