{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*179>}179{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The “chatos” or “sinoffering” was brought at any time for an unintentional sin that, had it 
