{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*188>}188{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The term “{\highlight7 @hh}{\highlight7 <HEB>}\rtlch \'f9\'d1\'c7\'e9{\highlight7 {\ltrch @ee}}{\highlight7 {\ltrch<}{\ltrch ENG}{\ltrch>}}\ltrch ” literally means gift. Here, it can refer to anything donated to the Temple, 
