{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*196>}196{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Shemos 21:16. In the “Midrash of the ten murdered martyrs” (version III) it is written, 
