{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*201>}201{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}In the Midrash (version III) it is written that Rabbi Yishmael asked the Angel Micha’el, 
