{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*203>}203{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The Midrash (version I) states that they beseeched Rabbi Yishmael to do so. In version II, 
